msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Yo! Hold up a sec, old man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Can I help you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Damn right. I'm in a real tight spot right now.\r\nHow 'bout you lend me your wallet for a bit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure about that.\r\nDoesn't sound like you'll be giving it back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Huh? I'm done playin' nice, asshole!\r\nGimme your goddamn money!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "S-Seriously!? I don't get it...\r\nHow'd this old dude beat us!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "What's with all the commotion?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "You're... You're that JUSTIS guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "R-Rainmaker...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Looks like we've got a real fighter here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Having some trouble handling him, are we?\r\nNeed me to tag in for a round?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "N-No thanks. We're good, seriously!\r\nPlease, we didn't wanna cause any trouble!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Anyways... We're outta here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "I'm picking up some intense vibes, from you...\r\nSimilar to that of a yakuza, yet not quite..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Perhaps... That's the life you left behind?\r\nAm I right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Just who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Me? I'm Komei of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS? That some new gang in town?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "\"Gang\" is not exactly the right word.\r\nIf anything, we were formed to destroy gangs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS is as the name implies<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>a gathering of\r\nlikeminded people determined to enact justice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Hm? Can't say you really look the part."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Is this gonna take all day, Komei?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Sorry, sorry. I tend to lose myself around such\r\ninteresting specimens. I'll be ready soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Hurry up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "That man is Kazuchika Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "He who makes money fall like rain...\r\nHence his moniker, Rainmaker."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "He is also the one who presides over\r\nthe 3,000 members of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "What? 3,000?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "You're surprised? With a 3,000 man army...\r\nIt should be clear we are not to be trifled with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Drawn in by his charisma, the troubled youths\r\nof today flock to join the ranks of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Here in the daunting streets of Kamurocho,\r\nwe give their rage direction and purpose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "If my hunch is correct, we will most certainly\r\ncross paths again soon. Until then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I come back and it's like the whole\r\nplace has gone nuts... This damn city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Take this! We ain't done with you yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "You probly thought you'd be able to run\r\nfrom us... but you thought wrong!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "You had this comin', Joe! Now stand up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "It's time ya set this right, yeah!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Huh? Hold on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "The hell're you lookin' at, grampa?\r\nBeat it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure what's going on here,\r\nbut that's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "You serious right now? You'd be better off\r\njust turnin' around now. You get me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Are you all right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Don't do this, old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "I'm telling you to run!\r\nTh-They're too strong..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Time's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "I'm sick of slow old fucks like you.\r\nGuess I'll have to move you myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Who are you guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Us? We're JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Me? I'm Komei from JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "We don't care who ya are, gramps.\r\nYou're goin' straight to hell!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "This is what happens when ya mess\r\nwith JUSTIS. Now die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Y-You saved me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Can you stand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I-I told you to run... but you stayed and fought.\r\nYou're incredible, old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "We should get you to a doctor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Not yet. For now, we need to run..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Joe-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Man, those JUSTIS bastards...\r\nHow could they do this to you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you a friend of his?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes! Uh, you're the one who\r\nhelped Joe-san out, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Um... Thank you very much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "It's all right. More importantly, we should get out of\r\nhere. We don't want to be here when more come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "R-Right! There's a restaurant we've been using\r\nas a meeting spot. We can head over there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "This seems like a strange place for a hideout."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "My sister's a part-timer here. I've grown to be\r\npretty good friends with the bartender, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Don't recall us ever becoming friends.\r\nSheesh, how'd my bar end up as your hideout?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "He looks a little soft, but the bartender here\r\nused to be a real rough dude."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Don't go spreading rumors about me. Sorry,\r\nthese guys are a real pain in the ass, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "It's all right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Um, Kiryu-san. Sorry about this. My brother and\r\nhis friend here are a real pain in the neck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Not at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Hey Masa, I'm gonna go buy some medicine for Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Right, thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Um... Kiryu-san, was it?\r\nI almost forgot<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>my name's Masao."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Joe-san... Er, Jojima-san and I went to grade school\r\ntogether. He was in sixth grade when I was in first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Joe-san's a big legend 'round here. He left Onomichi\r\nfor years... Only came back somewhat recently."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "And when he did... all the young punks\r\nin town couldn't have been more excited."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Joe-san went all the way to Tokyo,\r\nand came back an incredible man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "What do you mean...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "After all, he was one of the founders\r\nof JUSTIS up in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "I know what you're thinking. That those guys\r\nwho came for Joe-san earlier were JUSTIS, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I'm not entirely sure of the details myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "It doesn't seem like Joe-san managed\r\nto have a smooth break with the group, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "That's why day after day, JUSTIS members have\r\nbeen coming here to take Joe-san down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "They're coming all the way from\r\nKamurocho just for him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "You know, I ran into them up in Kamurocho, too.\r\nJust who are these JUSTIS guys...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "I see... So you're from Kamurocho..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Joe-san! Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Sorry about this, Masao."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "No, it's all right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "I've gotta thank you for earlier.\r\nIf you hadn't been there to help me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "...Who knows how things\r\nwould've turned out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "You're the only reason I'm still alive. But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I think by saving me, you put yourself\r\nin a real bad position."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "They've got eyes on you now.\r\nJUSTIS doesn't forget their grudges."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Wait, what? You saw Komei up\r\nin Kamurocho, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Yeah. We had a short chat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "I see. Komei's the JUSTIS strategist.\r\nHe's the leader Okada's right-hand man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. That guy was there with Komei.\r\nGoes by the name \"Rainmaker\" or something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "The one who makes it rain cash...\r\nHe's a key figure in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Kids who look up to him have formed an army\r\nand taken to the streets. That army is JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "But... Weren't you a founding officer?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "It didn't use to be like that\r\nback when it first started, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "A lot's happened, though. Okada and JUSTIS\r\nchanged, and now it's just a regular old street gang."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "And that's why you decided to leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Pretty much. I didn't think they'd chase me all\r\nthe way back to Onomichi, but that was naive of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "They're also not the only ones here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Apparently they've got over 100 guys here\r\nto chase me down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "And since you helped me fight against them...\r\nThey'll be coming for you, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Sorry for dragging you into this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "I'm not really sure who you are, but\r\nit's clear you've seen a fight or two."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Even so... 100 guys would overwhelm even\r\na great fighter. Get out of town while you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "I'm actually here on important business.\r\nI can't just up and leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Think about your safety!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "It's an unknown caller.\r\nProbably those thugs from earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "This is Joe.\r\nYeah, I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "No, that guy had nothing to do with me.\r\nHe doesn't know a thing about JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "What!? Hey, hold on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Joe-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Those bastards...\r\nThey took your sister."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Wait... What!? Sachiko!?\r\nYou can't be serious!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "They said we need to bring them\r\nKiryu-san if we want her back safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "Fine by me.\r\nTake me to them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Don't you understand what's happening?\r\nWe can't just hand you over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS doesn't mess around. I bet they have over\r\n100 guys here, all itching for a chance to kill you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "You're probably right.\r\nBut so what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "So you'd want to save her if there were only 10,\r\nbut you can't when there are 100? Is that it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "I don't care how many there are. Any scum\r\nwho'd take a girl hostage needs to get wiped up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "If you ask me...\r\nIsn't that what being a man's about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "I... I'll go round up some friends!\r\nAs many local punks as I can!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Masao..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "A complete stranger's gonna fight\r\nfor my little sister."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "As an Onomichi man, I can't just\r\nsit around and watch!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Hold on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "If you fight back..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS will keep sending soldiers from Tokyo\r\nuntil they destroy you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Just so we're clear, this is the biggest gang in Japan.\r\nDo you guys know what you're getting into!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "I guess we're just kinda dumb.\r\nBut I do know one thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "It doesn't matter how big their gang is.\r\nI'm not letting them stomp all over us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "I'm real sorry for dragging you into this.\r\nAnd for all the lame shit I've been spouting so far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Thanks to you and Kiryu-san,\r\nthe truth is clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "We've gotta go save Sachiko!\r\nAnd I'm gonna need you both!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Then let's prepare for war.\r\nWe should find anyone willing to lend a hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "We'll start scrounging a group together,\r\nso just let us know when you're ready, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "It's gonna take a little more time to get\r\na group together. Just wait a bit longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "We're ready to get going, Kiryu-san.\r\nAre you all set for the battle ahead?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Glad to hear it!\r\nAll right, let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Once you're ready,\r\nplease come let us know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Do you see them, Kiryu-san?\r\nThat's the JUSTIS army."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "How does it look?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "There's as many of them as I expected.\r\nThey must've known we'd try and fight back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "We've got a pretty big army too, though. There might\r\nbe more of them, but we can win if we're careful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Right. Well, let's go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Hold on a second."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Anyway, this is our fight, Kiryu-san.\r\nI don't want to pull you in too deep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Then what should I do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "But... now that I think about it,\r\nour team is pretty lacking in leadership."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "If we rush straight in without a plan,\r\nthey'll almost definitely crush us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "So, Kiryu-san... I was thinking maybe you\r\ncould be the guy giving the orders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "How would that work?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Well, you'll just need to watch over the battle\r\nand tell us what to do and when to do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "With your experience in battle, Kiryu-san,\r\nI'm sure this'll be a cinch..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "I prefer a more hands-on approach...\r\nBut fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS is your enemy.\r\nThis battle isn't mine to fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Thank you.\r\nOur enemy is strong and greater in number."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "I hope your leadership can overcome that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "Hmph. Nothing to worry about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Hey, they're here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "Heh, I'm surprised you guys came, knowing how\r\nmany of us there are. Not bad, Joe-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "My orders're coming from the top...\r\nSo no hard feelings, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "All right... Let's do this thing! Sachiko's\r\ncoming back to us! We're gonna win!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "We took care of all of them.\r\nYou're a real boss, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Same to you. I assumed you were weaker than\r\nthat since I've only ever seen you get beaten up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "Harsh, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "You bastards... Don't go thinking you can\r\nget away after what you did to my men!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "Don't you know about JUSTIS? With the thousands\r\nof soldiers we have... We're unstoppable!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "I used to believe that was the case,\r\nbut this man showed me the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "It doesn't matter if I think I'm gonna win or not.\r\nThat's not how I should decide what to do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "After all... I'm a man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Hmph..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "What the hell're you talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Our orders're coming from the top.\r\nWe're gonna crush you one way or another!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "I wish I didn't have to resort to this kinda\r\nviolence, but I don't got a choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Let me help, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "I could use the exercise. Shake some rust off.\r\nBesides, I want to teach these lowlife punks a lesson."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "All right.\r\nLet's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS isn't gonna stand for this.\r\nYou bastards... It's time to die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "Well, guess we can't back down now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "Are you regretting this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "No. If anything, it helped make things clear.\r\nI'm through living my life in fear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "I've decided...\r\nJUSTIS is going down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "And as for Rainmaker...\r\nI'll make him see the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "Did Masao tell you I was\r\none of JUSTIS's founding officers?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Yeah, more or less."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Back in the day, he and I were the best of friends.\r\nKamurocho was our regular stomping ground."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "But at the time, the city was full of young thugs\r\nrepping gangs in specific colors..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Guys like Bloody Eye and Blue Z..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "Young as they were,\r\nthe color gangs ruled the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho was theirs and theirs alone.\r\nYou couldn't breathe without their permission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "They were pretty annoyed that Rainmaker\r\nand I refused to join them, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "So in return, they started attacking our friends.\r\nAll to get us to join their dumb little gangs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "Okada and I weren't going to take that lying down,\r\nthough. That's why we decided to fight back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "That's why we formed JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Though I've gotta say, JUSTIS is looking more\r\nand more like a shitty color clone every day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "So an organization formed to destroy a gang has\r\nturned into a gang itself... Ironic, I'd say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Since I helped organize them,\r\nit's up to me to help shut them down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "So, what happens now?\r\nAre you gonna try and stop them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Now that we've meddled with their plans,\r\nJUSTIS won't rest until we're dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "They'll probably send the Six Lunatics after us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "The Six Lunatics...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "They're the leaders of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "In order to strengthen the organization, Okada\r\nthrew some money around and brought them in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "They might be strong, but they all\r\nhave some kinda shady past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "Ever since they joined, JUSTIS has steadily\r\ntransformed into a terrible gang."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "The Six Lunatics, huh?\r\nAre they really that powerful?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "From what I can tell, each one of them\r\nis just as strong a fighter as you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Huh? As strong as Kiryu-san...?\r\nNo way...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "Didn't you see him fight?\r\nYou did see him fight, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "...Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Why did we have to make enemies outta\r\nthose guys!? We'll never win against them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "You're the one who started it! I thought you\r\ndidn't wanna back down, no matter what!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "The Six Lunatics..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "My dear Six Lunatics. We are all present, yes?\r\nIt seems we've run into a minor snag."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "What kinda snag're you talkin' about?\r\nJust get on with it. I'm busy here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "Did the cops nab one of our boys?\r\nI'm right, ain't I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "You're in for a real bruisin'\r\nif that's all this is, Komei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "It's because of Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Hm? How did you know that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "I heard you put a crew together\r\nand went to go take him out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "What were you thinking, Komei?\r\nThat's not your call to make."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "Okada told us to leave Joe alone.\r\nYou in the habit of disobeying orders now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "Let's cool it, guys.\r\nIt's no problemo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "People've gotta pay the price for cutting\r\nties with an organization like us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "That applies to Joe, too. He might be a founder,\r\nbut he doesn't get a free pass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS is a huge organization, remember.\r\nWe've gotta set the right example."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "You've got a point there. So?\r\nWhat's this little snag we hit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "In short..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "Joe managed to defeat a large squadron\r\nI had sent out to destroy him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "After his defection, Joe returned\r\nto his hometown of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "It appears as though some local friends\r\nof his helped push our forces back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "This is no minor snag, Komei.\r\nIt's a total failure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "You're draggin' the JUSTIS name through the mud!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "M-My apologies..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Yano."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "Here are some funds."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I need you down in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "C'mon, me again?\r\nGuess I can't say no, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "But if there's any cash left... \r\nI'm ain't gonna hesitate to hit the town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "Fine by me. However... You're one of\r\nthe Six Lunatics. Failure isn't an option."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "If ya screw this one up,\r\nI'll be happy to kick your ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "What he means is, you're outta the group\r\nif you fail. Them's JUSTIS rules."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "I already know that, so shut the hell up.\r\nDon't recall asking for a reminder."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Welp, guess I'll start packin' my things.\r\nMaybe I should get a travel book!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "You really messed this up, Joe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "You wanna form a new team!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "Yeah. JUSTIS is gonna send the Six Lunatics\r\nafter us, without a doubt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "If we want to fight them off, we'll need to\r\ngather an army and form a defense force."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "Right... I guess we can't turn back now.\r\nLet's do it! My mind's made up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "All right, let's make a new team with Joe as our\r\nleader! We're gonna be even bigger than JUSTIS!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "No, I'm no leader anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "Huh? But then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "Y-You can't mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san.\r\nWill you be our leader?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "You want me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "Yeah. JUSTIS is massive, so we're gonna need\r\na team just as big if we want to fight them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "I'm not too keen on managing people, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "Besides, I'm responsible for this in the first place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "With me at the helm... there's no way we'd ever\r\nbe able to actually bring JUSTIS down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "Plus, we almost definitely would've lost that\r\nbattle earlier if we didn't have your leadership."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "If we wanna win...\r\nWe need your guidance, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "Please... Lend us your strength!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "I appreciate the offer, but there are other\r\nthings I need to be taking care of right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "To be honest... I just don't have the time\r\nfor this conflict of yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "I figured you would say that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "But it really would be better if you stuck\r\naround with us, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "And why's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "Because, well... JUSTIS is gonna stop\r\nat nothing now to make sure you end up dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "They'll keep sending team after team\r\nof men to hunt you down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "You can't take them all on alone.\r\nEven you would wear down eventually."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Sorry for dragging you into this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "But I agree with Masao."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "You should probably stay with us...\r\nAt least to protect yourself from them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Come on..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "Please. I know you're busy, but I need to set\r\nthings right. I need to wake Okada up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "He's, well... He's my best friend. I know he's\r\nlost sight of his goals, but I can't abandon him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "That hits close to home..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "324||||4"
msgid "All right, then. I'll help you out.\r\nNow lift your head back up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "Seriously!? This is great, Joe-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "As you said, it would be a real problem\r\nif I had to deal with JUSTIS alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "Besides... I can understand how you\r\nmight feel about that friend of yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thanks a ton. With you by\r\nour side... this team's gonna be unstoppable!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "330||||4"
msgid "All right! We're gonna make the best team\r\never with Kiryu-san as our leader!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "Oh! What do we wanna do about our name?\r\nSomething cool would be good, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "Wait, we need a name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "Think about it. Every famous team\r\nhas to be recognizable somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "We've gotta make sure ours is good, though.\r\nMaybe we could use English like JUSTIS did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "Hm... We should probably let our leader decide."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "Me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "338||||4"
msgid "Yeah. You're the head of our team, Kiryu-san,\r\nso our name should represent that somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "We could go with K-2016. Or the Kiryu Revolution\r\nArmy! That might be too old-school, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "Hm... A team name that includes my own..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "What about the Kiryu Clan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "342||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu Clan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "What's wrong with that? I thought these kinds\r\nof groups were always clans or families."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "It's not that weird, really."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah, I guess you're not wrong...\r\nBut it's pretty yakuza sounding..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "Well, I think it's great.\r\nOur leader has some excellent taste."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "You can't be serious..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "This is the beginning of the Kiryu Clan,\r\nthe ones who will bring JUSTIS to its knees."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "Not only are we gonna protect our hometown\r\nof Onomichi... But we're gonna wake Okada up, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "351||||4"
msgid "All right! Let's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "Heh... Here goes nothing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "So... I know I'm the team leader,\r\nbut what exactly does that entail?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "354||||4"
msgid "Give us orders in battle, Kiryu-san.\r\nJust like what you did for us earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "355||||4"
msgid "Beyond that... It's up to you\r\nto organize the Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "Organize it...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "Yes. We don't have many members at the moment,\r\nbut we'll start growing any minute now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "And when we do, we'll need a strong leader to\r\nkeep things orderly. That's where you come in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "359||||4"
msgid "You'll need to put your strength to good use and\r\norganize the team to be most efficient, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "360||||4"
msgid "Hey, why do I have to do everything...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "Don't worry about it. Just make positions\r\nand assign people like at a company."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "I don't really understand how that stuff works...\r\nBut it would be great if you could do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "...Fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "But I have a pretty biased understanding of the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I'll probably structure our team based on\r\nmy former workplace. Think that would be okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "Yeah, whatever you wanna do! By the way,\r\nKiryu-san, where exactly did you work?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "Heh... Best that you don't know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? Eh, fine by me.\r\nNow then, it's up to you to organize the Kiryu Clan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "If you ever want to start a mission or change\r\nthe team structure, just let me know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "This is real bad, Kiryu-san!\r\nJUSTIS is sending a swarm of guys our way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "So they're finally fighting back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "There shouldn't be too many here yet.\r\nLet's attack now while we still can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "373||||4"
msgid "Totally! We're gonna wreck 'em!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "All right... Let's move."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "Look at how many guys they've\r\nalready sent down here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376||||4"
msgid "Compared to the full JUSTIS\r\nnumbers, this is nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "377||||4"
msgid "If we can't win this little skirmish,\r\nthe war is good as lost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "I already knew they were strong...\r\nbut JUSTIS is even tougher than I imagined."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "Maybe, but we still have to take them down.\r\nIt doesn't matter who they are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380||||4"
msgid "That's what men do, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "Yeah, something like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "Anyway, that's enough talk.\r\nCome on... Let's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "Gotcha!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "Aw yeah! Kiryu-san, Joe-san!\r\nWe did it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "Looks like we're at least strong enough\r\nto take down some two-bit thugs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "387||||4"
msgid "Bravo, bravo!\r\nExcellent work, you guys!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "That voice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "I knew it... Yano."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "391||||4"
msgid "Long time no see, Joe-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "Didn't think you'd go runnin' back home.\r\nKinda pathetic, don't ya think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "Who is this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "So you're old man Kiryu, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "395||||4"
msgid "Nice to meet ya! I'm one of the most\r\ntalented producers for JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "That's my name.\r\nIt's a pleasure to meet ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "What's this guy's deal?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "399||||4"
msgid "He's one of the Six Lunatics, Toru Yano. He's\r\ncalled the \"raid commander\" over at JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400||||4"
msgid "He used to be an expert thief and fraudster,\r\nat least until Okada took him in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "Now he's the guy in charge of all their petty crimes.\r\nA horrible, deceitful man, if you ask me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "402||||4"
msgid "Whoa, whoa, whoa! That's pretty\r\nnasty stuff to say about an old friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "Besides, I thought I just said I'm a producer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "I work day and night producin' methods for\r\nthe younger boys to bring in cash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "Producer, my ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "406||||4"
msgid "You know how many people've gotten\r\nsent to prison because of you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "Don't gimme that!\r\nYou're thinking too small!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "The only reason JUSTIS is profitin' is\r\nbecause I'm rakin' in the dough, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "I don't care about their profits.\r\nYou're here to fight us, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Now, now. Chill out, bro. I just got here.\r\nI'm not lookin' to fight just yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "I mean, it's my first time in Onomichi. I was\r\nthinkin' I'd grab some ramen and take in the sights."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "I'm down to spare you guys...\r\nFor the time bein'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "By the way, these fools you just beat\r\nwere just a nice little sampler for ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "From now on it's going to\r\nbe wave after wave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "Hope ya tire yourselves out tryin'\r\nto deal with all of 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "And once you're nice n' exhausted,\r\nI'll come in and take out the trash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "417||||4"
msgid "You bastard...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "418||||4"
msgid "I ain't like the other Lunatics. I'm smart, y'know.\r\nThat's just how I do things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "Anyway, try to stay alive 'til\r\nI'm ready for ya, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "That guy really pisses me off.\r\nIs he seriously that tough?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "422||||4"
msgid "He is. His appearance hides his true skill.\r\nIf we want to beat him, we'll need to prepare."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "Hot damn, you guys're kinda tough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "Yano..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "Oh! Glad you remembered me.\r\nThat's my name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428||||4"
msgid "Sorry to keep ya waitin', Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "429||||4"
msgid "I wasn't holding my breath."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "C'monnn, man. Eh, whatevs.\r\nI just stopped by today for my last warning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "431||||4"
msgid "My whirlwind tour of Onomichi's finally over.\r\nIt's goddamn beautiful here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "Makes sense that your bastard friend Joe\r\nwould run for his life to a place like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "You..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "434||||4"
msgid "I wish I could relax a bit more, but the Lunatics\r\nkeep yappin' about how I need to hurry things up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "435||||4"
msgid "Next time we meet, you're gonna be up against me.\r\nThat'll be the day y'all die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436||||4"
msgid "Ya better be ready for the Six Lunatics.\r\nThe hammer of JUSTIS is comin' down on you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "437||||4"
msgid "You're not gonna know what hit ya!\r\nFools!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "438||||4"
msgid "So Yano is our next opponent..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "439||||4"
msgid "Yeah. He's strong, but the Kiryu Clan\r\nhas grown a lot stronger lately, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440||||4"
msgid "Let's take him down, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "441||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "442||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano... He's no ordinary man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "443||||4"
msgid "It's finally time for our fight against Yano.\r\nHe's gonna be miles ahead of our competition so far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Let's give this all we've got!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "445||||4"
msgid "Yeah, let's get going. It's time we show\r\nhim what true strength looks like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "446||||4"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "447||||4"
msgid "Gotcha!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "448||||4"
msgid "It's about time y'all showed, Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "449||||4"
msgid "I hope you're ready for us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "450||||4"
msgid "If we manage to bring Yano down, that should\r\nstrike a huge blow right to the heart of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "451||||4"
msgid "Beating one of the Six Lunatics will be\r\na stepping stone for our future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452||||4"
msgid "If we can win this... who knows what'll happen.\r\nLet's give this everything we have, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "453||||4"
msgid "Yeah. We've let this guy run his mouth at us\r\nfor long enough. It's time we shut him up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "454||||4"
msgid "Y'all ready? We are..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "455||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "457||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "458||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "459||||4"
msgid "Kill them all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "460||||4"
msgid "Here we go. Kiryu Clan, move out!\r\nLet's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "461||||4"
msgid "All right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "462||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "463||||4"
msgid "I don't get it...\r\nWe had way more guys than you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464||||4"
msgid "You've lost, Yano. This town is our home.\r\nNow take your men and get out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "465||||4"
msgid "It ain't gonna be that easy to make me leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "466||||4"
msgid "Loss isn't an option for one of the Six Lunatics.\r\nIf I went back now, they'd totally kick me out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "467||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I'm gonna have to kick your\r\nguys' asses. That's my only choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "469||||4"
msgid "Playtime's over, buddy. Time to show ya\r\nthe real might of the Six Lunatics!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "470||||4"
msgid "Here I come!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "471||||4"
msgid "The hell, man?\r\nHow're you so strong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "472||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! We beat one of the Six Lunatics!\r\nWe took down Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "473||||4"
msgid "Mhm. I bet this'll ruffle\r\nJUSTIS's feathers a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "474||||4"
msgid "You really think losing Yano'll make us sweat?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "475||||4"
msgid "If anything... you're the hombre\r\nunder pressure here, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "476||||4"
msgid "You're..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "477||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo, Joe!\r\nChill out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "478||||4"
msgid "Is he another one of the Lunatics?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "479||||4"
msgid "That's another Lunatic... Naito.\r\nThey say he's just as strong as Okada himself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "480||||4"
msgid "I can't believe they're already\r\nthrowing Naito at us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "481||||4"
msgid "Excuse me? Look here. Don't go making it\r\nsound like I got ordered to come here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "482||||4"
msgid "I'm here 'cause I wanna be here.\r\nNobody told me to do it. Not even Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "483||||4"
msgid "Truth is, I've got a reason for\r\ntrekking all the way to Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "484||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... That reason is you.\r\nYou're a muy interesante fellow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "485||||4"
msgid "Me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "486||||4"
msgid "The former Tojo Clan fourth chairman, and\r\nthe renowned Dragon of Dojima... Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "487||||4"
msgid "Huh!? The Tojo Clan? Um, Kiryu-san...\r\nYou're in the yakuza?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488||||4"
msgid "Used to be.\r\nI'm just a civilian now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "489||||4"
msgid "I've got tons of yakuza and mafia amigos floating\r\naround, so the name Kiryu immediately rang a bell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "490||||4"
msgid "In case you forgot... I'm Naito.\r\nBuenas noches, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "492||||4"
msgid "Guess you and me don't gel too good, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "493||||4"
msgid "The legends about you are muy grande, though.\r\nEvery time I hear one, I feel like I'm gonna puke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "494||||4"
msgid "Guys like you and Joe are the worst. Always trying\r\nto act the hero for some bullshit sense of honor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "495||||4"
msgid "I've always wanted to knock you guys down a peg.\r\nNever thought I'd actually get the chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "496||||4"
msgid "So you want to fight?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "497||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo, Kiryu-san!\r\nChill out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "498||||4"
msgid "Didn't you just finish fighting Yano? It'd be way too\r\nboring to beat you when you're not at your peak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "499||||4"
msgid "Besides, I'm not interested in just fighting\r\none-on-one with no clear purpose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500||||4"
msgid "I'd rather squash all your little friends... then\r\ntake my sweet time with the head honcho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "501||||4"
msgid "Adios."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "502||||4"
msgid "Wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "503||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "504||||4"
msgid "Your friend is hurt here.\r\nAt least take him with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "506||||4"
msgid "Huh. Y'know, friend is way too strong a word.\r\nBesides, we don't need failures in the Lunatics."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "507||||4"
msgid "No point bringing him back now.\r\nMight as well end things clean and simple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "508||||4"
msgid "You bastard... Naito..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "509||||4"
msgid "Don't do it, Naito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "510||||4"
msgid "You never change, Joe. Okada's the same way.\r\nSeriously makes me wanna barf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "511||||4"
msgid "Looks like Kiryu's not gonna be flying solo\r\nin the afterlife now. You get to join him, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512||||4"
msgid "You'll see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "513||||4"
msgid "Naito..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "514||||4"
msgid "I just can't believe you're\r\nreally a famous yakuza, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "515||||4"
msgid "It's all in the past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "516||||4"
msgid "But you were some kinda chairman, right?\r\nNo surprise you're good at leading a team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "517||||4"
msgid "We trust you no matter what, Kiryu-san.\r\nYour past life doesn't change that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "518||||4"
msgid "If anything, I'm glad to know you're on our side\r\nand not theirs. We have a lot to learn from you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "519||||4"
msgid "I'm not all that special.\r\nYou shouldn't put me on a pedestal like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "520||||4"
msgid "That's a lot of bull! Have a bit more\r\nconfidence in yourself, Kiryu-chan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "521||||4"
msgid "You sure about this? I dunno if I really\r\nwant this guy on our team..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "522||||4"
msgid "It's fine by me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "523||||4"
msgid "He did say he was turning over a new leaf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "524||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! JUSTIS is the worst of the worst! I knew\r\nKiryu-chan was my man the moment we locked fists!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "525||||4"
msgid "We're gonna make a great team!\r\nGood shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "526||||4"
msgid "This guy is bonkers..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "527||||4"
msgid "He's definitely strong, though. If we want\r\nto beat Naito, we'll need people like him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "528||||4"
msgid "I got this. I don't feel a shred of remorse about\r\nJUSTIS, by the way. It's nothing but hate now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "529||||4"
msgid "I mean, I'm a proud dude.\r\nI'll do whatever it takes to bring 'em down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "530||||4"
msgid "Right. I appreciate the help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "531||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!\r\nI'm on the case!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "532||||4"
msgid "As for our next guy, Naito... Apparently he's got\r\na pretty crazy number of followers on his side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "533||||4"
msgid "He was saying he's got ties to mafia and yakuza\r\ngroups, too. Pretty shady, if you ask me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "534||||4"
msgid "I dunno what he's doin' with the Lunatics...\r\nBut apparently Okada pays him the big bucks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "535||||4"
msgid "His group's way different than the rat pack\r\nI shuffled on down here with, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "536||||4"
msgid "Ya better watch your backs. Things're gonna\r\nget tough if you don't prepare for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "537||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "538||||4"
msgid "Not bad, though unsurprising from the fourth chairman.\r\nFor the time you've had, your team is muy bueno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "539||||4"
msgid "Naito..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "540||||4"
msgid "At first these little battles were real entertaining.\r\nBut now... they're just starting to bore me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "541||||4"
msgid "So the next one's gonna be the last."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "542||||4"
msgid "If you guys manage to beat me...\r\nI'll take JUSTIS forces out of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "543||||4"
msgid "You mean it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "544||||4"
msgid "Si. No way you're gonna win against me, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "545||||4"
msgid "I've just been messing with you guys so far.\r\nI'm gonna give you all I got from now on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "546||||4"
msgid "Once I take your newly formed team down a notch,\r\nyou're all gonna be muy muerto. I can see it now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "547||||4"
msgid "I can't wait to make it happen for real."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "548||||4"
msgid "Hey, Naito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "549||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "550||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "551||||4"
msgid "Chill out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "552||||4"
msgid "You bastard... Just you wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "553||||4"
msgid "So our next battle is a showdown with Naito.\r\nWe need to make sure we're ready to rumble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "554||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "555||||4"
msgid "It's just about time to take on Naito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "556||||4"
msgid "He said he'd pull outta Onomichi if we win...\r\nYou think he meant it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "557||||4"
msgid "I would assume he did.\r\nHe's not the kinda guy to go back on his word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "558||||4"
msgid "Besides, JUSTIS would have no business sending guys\r\ndown here with both Naito and Yano out of the picture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "559||||4"
msgid "They shouldn't even be sending guys down to\r\nOnomichi in that kinda situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "560||||4"
msgid "They'll probably just focus on solidifying\r\ntheir forces in Kamurocho instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "561||||4"
msgid "Right. Guess we'd just had to focus on\r\nthose remaining guys after that, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "562||||4"
msgid "Sounds like this is a major turning point, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "563||||4"
msgid "That's right.\r\nWe need to win this, no matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "564||||4"
msgid "All right, everyone.\r\nIt's time we move out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "565||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! We're gonna smoosh Naito\r\nlike a dumb little bug! C'mon, you guys!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "566||||4"
msgid "R-Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "567||||4"
msgid "Buenas noches!\r\nKiryu-san, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "568||||4"
msgid "We're here, just like you asked.\r\nNow let's finish this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "569||||4"
msgid "No need to remind me. I remember."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "570||||4"
msgid "As a sign of my respect to you,\r\nI brought along my elite squad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "571||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but this is the Kiryu Clan's last fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "572||||4"
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "573||||4"
msgid "Bring it on.\r\nLet's get this fiesta started!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "574||||4"
msgid "Huh, I didn't think you'd be this strong.\r\nGuess I underestimated you a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "575||||4"
msgid "Now then...\r\nHow about a one-on-one with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "576||||4"
msgid "That's what you wanted, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "577||||4"
msgid "You sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "578||||4"
msgid "You've still got hombres left standing. It'd be\r\neasier for you to just come at me with everyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "579||||4"
msgid "That's not really my style. I'd rather fight\r\nwith honor than crush you unfairly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "580||||4"
msgid "Aha. So that must be what keeps\r\ndrawing all these people to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "581||||4"
msgid "I've gotta say, you make me sick.\r\nBut I'm no idiota. I'll take you up on your offer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "582||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... It's time to fight, mano a mano."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "583||||4"
msgid "Right. Let's get it over with, Naito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "584||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo! Chill out, Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "587||||4"
msgid "Oh my god!\r\nKiryu-san, you beat Naito!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "588||||4"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "589||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I think so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "590||||4"
msgid "I totally lost...\r\nYou're really something, Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "591||||4"
msgid "You promised. \r\nPull your JUSTIS goons out of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "592||||4"
msgid "Don't worry about that. With Yano and I beat, JUSTIS\r\nwon't have the cajones to be sending guys down here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "593||||4"
msgid "Besides, a promise is a promise.\r\nThe Onomichi invasion's over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "594||||4"
msgid "All right! We protected Onomichi,\r\njust like we set out to do!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "595||||4"
msgid "All we can do now is head up to Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "596||||4"
msgid "Okada... I'm coming for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "597||||4"
msgid "All right. Let's head back to the hideout\r\nand plan our next attack."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "598||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "599||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "600||||4"
msgid "Uh... Take me with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "601||||4"
msgid "What was that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "602||||4"
msgid "I used to think I couldn't stand self-righteous,\r\nchivalrous bastards like you and Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "603||||4"
msgid "But y'know, beneath that hate...\r\nwas admiration."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "604||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nI wanna learn to be more like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "605||||4"
msgid "Let me join you guys.\r\nI wanna be your pareja."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "606||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "607||||4"
msgid "Naito on our team? Who knows when\r\nhe'd turn on us. I can't trust him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "608||||4"
msgid "No, he's being genuine. I get how\r\nhe can be so drawn to Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "609||||4"
msgid "Joe-san, I didn't know you swing that way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "610||||4"
msgid "D-Don't be an ass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "611||||4"
msgid "I'm not really sure what pareja means...\r\nbut you can come along if you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "612||||4"
msgid "We'll be heading to Kamurocho next.\r\nUntil then, try to heal up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "613||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "614||||4"
msgid "Chill out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "615||||4"
msgid "Chill out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "618||||4"
msgid "It appears Naito has fallen as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "619||||4"
msgid "I see. Figures."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "620||||4"
msgid "Shall we reconvene the whole\r\nof our army here in Kamurocho, then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "621||||4"
msgid "Yes, get started.\r\nThe battle's moving to our home turf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "622||||4"
msgid "But it's just the beginning.\r\nSo let's make sure... they get a warm welcome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "623||||4"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "624||||4"
msgid "Joe... Kazuma Kiryu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "625||||4"
msgid "Okada and Komei are the only ones left now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "626||||4"
msgid "They're up in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "627||||4"
msgid "Next time you head up there,\r\nwe'll gladly join you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "628||||4"
msgid "When you have the chance,\r\nstop by the hideout in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "629||||4"
msgid "Looks like Onomichi's gonna be okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "630||||4"
msgid "The rest of the Six Lunatics are gonna\r\nbe waiting for us up in Kamurocho, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "631||||4"
msgid "Next time you head up there,\r\nwe'll gladly join you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "632||||4"
msgid "When you have the chance,\r\nstop by the hideout in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "633||||4"
msgid "Looks like Onomichi's gonna be okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "634||||4"
msgid "The rest of the Six Lunatics are gonna\r\nbe waiting for us up in Kamurocho, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "635||||4"
msgid "We don't know exactly when we're\r\ngonna have the chance to head up there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "636||||4"
msgid "But for now, we should focus on building up\r\nthe team down here in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "637||||4"
msgid "We'd probably get our butts kicked in a second\r\nif we head up there without any preparation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "638||||4"
msgid "You're right. We should make sure we're\r\nready before we bring the team up to Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "639||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "640||||4"
msgid "Joe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "641||||4"
msgid "I could tell that was you from a mile away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "642||||4"
msgid "Hold on, are you living here\r\nin the Navy Apartments, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "643||||4"
msgid "I am. By the way, are you sure\r\nyou should be out and about like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "644||||4"
msgid "It's not too big a deal, I don't think.\r\nWhat are you up to, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "645||||4"
msgid "Well... I'm about to head up to Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "646||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "647||||4"
msgid "I'm leaving tomorrow.\r\nI'll be out of Onomichi for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "648||||4"
msgid "Hold on, but Kamurocho...\r\nThat's where JUSTIS is based, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "649||||4"
msgid "This has nothing to do with them.\r\nI have other business I need to take care of."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "650||||4"
msgid "Oh. In that case..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "651||||4"
msgid "Is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "652||||4"
msgid "No, I was just thinking of you spending time\r\nup in Kamurocho. It gave me an idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "653||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "654||||4"
msgid "Well, I should go tell Masao and the others\r\nwhat you're gonna be up to. Later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "655||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Good to see you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "656||||4"
msgid "What the? Joe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "657||||4"
msgid "What are you doing here?\r\nI don't understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "658||||4"
msgid "We were gonna have to make our way on up\r\nto Kamurocho at one point or another, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "659||||4"
msgid "Coming up at the same time as you made the most\r\nsense. It was easy to get everyone on board, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "660||||4"
msgid "Everyone's here...?\r\nCome on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "661||||4"
msgid "Isn't that a good thing?\r\nIt means we're all serious about this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "662||||4"
msgid "Speaking of, we got hold of a store\r\nwe can use as a hideout while we're up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "663||||4"
msgid "It's a little shop inside the Millennium Tower\r\nbuilding called the M Side Cafe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "664||||4"
msgid "Want to go see it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "665||||4"
msgid "I guess I have to...\r\nJust for a bit, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "666||||4"
msgid "This is a pretty swanky place.\r\nAre you sure we'll be okay here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "667||||4"
msgid "Well, the bartender down at La Pente apparently\r\nknows the owner. He helped negotiate for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "668||||4"
msgid "Seriously?\r\nWhat's up with that guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "669||||4"
msgid "I wonder..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "670||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "671||||4"
msgid "Look what the cat dragged in!\r\nYou're really here, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "672||||4"
msgid "It's you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "673||||4"
msgid "Ya can't hide from us.\r\nWe know your every move, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "674||||4"
msgid "And you took time out of your day to welcome us?\r\nThat's a real nice gesture of you. Appreciate it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "675||||4"
msgid "Joe. Now that you've come to Kamurocho,\r\ndon't expect any mercy from us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "676||||4"
msgid "This is JUSTIS's home base. You won't have\r\nthe same freedom here as you did in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "677||||4"
msgid "We know damn well where your base is.\r\nWe wouldn't be here otherwise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "678||||4"
msgid "Anyway... Whaddya say?\r\nLet's fight, you and me. Like old times."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "679||||4"
msgid "Heh... Nope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "680||||4"
msgid "This man is the renowned Rainmaker, remember?\r\nHe has no time for an insignificant whelp like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "681||||4"
msgid "Besides... You have others in line waiting to fight you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "682||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "683||||4"
msgid "Don't go forgettin' about us, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "684||||4"
msgid "You get to deal with us next time.\r\nI've been damn bored lately. Entertain me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "685||||4"
msgid "Tenzan, Kojima..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "686||||4"
msgid "Hey, Joe. Who are these guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "687||||4"
msgid "The Six Lunatics tag team, Tenzan and Kojima.\r\nTenCozy for short."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "688||||4"
msgid "They're part of the reason Okada and I formed\r\nJUSTIS to begin with. They were in the colors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "689||||4"
msgid "The color gangs?\r\nHow did they end up working with JUSTIS?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "690||||4"
msgid "Okada probably paid through the nose for them.\r\nThey're real assholes, but they're definitely strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "691||||4"
msgid "Each is tough alone, but their power\r\nmultiplies when you pair them together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "692||||4"
msgid "That's why they're TenCozy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "693||||4"
msgid "Not bad, Joe-kun.\r\nSounds like ya know your shit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "694||||4"
msgid "You're right. We might've switched over to the side\r\nof JUSTIS, but we'll always be champs! Forever!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "695||||4"
msgid "One plus one don't make two. For us, one plus one\r\nis two hundred! That's ten times better! Ten times!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "696||||4"
msgid "Hey... You wanna check that math?\r\nShouldn't it be one hundred times better?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "697||||4"
msgid "I don't care for your lip!\r\nIt's just a crapton more than two, alright!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "698||||4"
msgid "If you're really givin' me shit for this,\r\nI'd be glad to rip ya a new one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "699||||4"
msgid "Try me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "700||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "701||||4"
msgid "Now, now. We cannot allow one of our mighty\r\nSix Lunatics to sully himself with this garbage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "702||||4"
msgid "Stooping to his level is not the desired\r\noutcome. Isn't that right, Rainmaker?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "703||||4"
msgid "Yeah, true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "704||||4"
msgid "Though come to think of it,\r\nhave we met before?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "705||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I think we have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "706||||4"
msgid "Heh... What a coincidence this is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "707||||4"
msgid "I have no ill will toward you... But if you\r\ntry to stop me, I'll crush you where you stand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "708||||4"
msgid "Try me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "709||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS is the sole dominant force\r\nin Kamurocho at this point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "710||||4"
msgid "It's been ages since we've had a good fight.\r\nThis should be exciting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "711||||4"
msgid "I hope you provide us with some\r\nentertainment, Kiryu Clan. We must be off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "712||||4"
msgid "Watch your backs, bastards."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "713||||4"
msgid "So those are the leaders of JUSTIS.\r\nSounds like more fights on the horizon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "714||||4"
msgid "Right. Anyway, this place is gonna be our\r\nhideout while we're up in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "715||||4"
msgid "Come talk to me if you want to reorganize\r\nthe team or start a battle against JUSTIS, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "716||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "717||||4"
msgid "You're actually kinda strong, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "718||||4"
msgid "It's been forever since I've had to put my all\r\ninto fightin' someone. Feels good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "719||||4"
msgid "Still, we're gonna have to settle this soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "720||||4"
msgid "Hey, Tenzan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "721||||4"
msgid "We're gonna finish ya guys off next time.\r\nCome at us with all ya got, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "722||||4"
msgid "Me n' Kojima, the TenCozy tag team,\r\nare gonna dice y'all into tiny little pieces."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "723||||4"
msgid "I don't care if I have to fight one or both of you.\r\nLet's just hurry up and get it over with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "724||||4"
msgid "Don't ya remember? For us, one plus one\r\nain't two. It's two hundred."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "725||||4"
msgid "I remember. One plus one is two hundred.\r\nTen times more than normal, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "726||||4"
msgid "Glad ya understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "727||||4"
msgid "We're gonna be puttin' all our effort into\r\nthis fight, so ya better return the favor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "728||||4"
msgid "This JUSTIS bullshit ain't really our\r\ncup of tea, if I'm bein' honest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "729||||4"
msgid "If we get good fights outta it,\r\nthat's all that matters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "730||||4"
msgid "Ya guys better make it interesting.\r\nIf this's just another borin' slog..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "731||||4"
msgid "...We'll slaughter every last one of ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "732||||4"
msgid "So the TenCozy tag team is up next.\r\nThey won't be an easy opponent."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "733||||4"
msgid "Let's make sure we're ready\r\nbefore we fight them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "734||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "735||||4"
msgid "So we're finally going up\r\nagainst Tenzan and Kojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "736||||4"
msgid "Yeah. They're both strong on their own,\r\nbut their power multiplies when they're together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "737||||4"
msgid "It's not gonna be as smooth as the other\r\nLunatics. We need to be ready."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "738||||4"
msgid "Make sure you keep a careful eye on\r\ntheir movements, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "739||||4"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "740||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho is JUSTIS's home base, remember.\r\nThings'll be way rougher than in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "741||||4"
msgid "But if we can manage to win, that should really\r\nshake some things up in their organization."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "742||||4"
msgid "Once we win here, JUSTIS is gonna be totally\r\non the ropes. Let's give this all we got!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "743||||4"
msgid "Got it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "744||||4"
msgid "Glad to see ya here, Joe. I was thinkin'\r\nyou'd run with your tail between your legs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "745||||4"
msgid "I'm not afraid of an idiot like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "746||||4"
msgid "We're gonna beat you, then take down Okada,\r\nand destroy JUSTIS while we're at it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "747||||4"
msgid "Ya sure you can do that? You've never won\r\na single fight against Okada, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "748||||4"
msgid "Not yet I haven't.\r\nThings have changed, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "749||||4"
msgid "Look at that.\r\nYou grew into a real bold little shit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "750||||4"
msgid "Fine. Show us how strong ya are now.\r\nIf ya want Okada, you gotta go through us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "751||||4"
msgid "We've beaten every last one of your men.\r\nNow just surrender, nice and easy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "752||||4"
msgid "Surrender?\r\nThe hell're you sayin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "753||||4"
msgid "Group battles ain't our bag. We're not too big\r\non commandin' other people, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "754||||4"
msgid "We prefer talkin' with our fists.\r\nThat's the best way to settle shit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "755||||4"
msgid "What he's sayin' is... we're just gettin' started."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "756||||4"
msgid "We only got two of us left at this point,\r\nbut us two're all we need."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "757||||4"
msgid "That's how the TenCozy tag team rolls!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "758||||4"
msgid "Not bad. You know,\r\nI actually don't mind you guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "759||||4"
msgid "I have to agree. I'd much rather settle\r\nthings in a man-to-man fight, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "760||||4"
msgid "Perfect. How 'bout it, then?\r\nYou guys wanna throw down?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "761||||4"
msgid "You n' Joe versus me n' Tenzan.\r\nIt'll be a four man deathmatch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "762||||4"
msgid "Sounds good to me.\r\nHow about you, Joe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "763||||4"
msgid "You don't even have to ask.\r\nIf they wanna fight, I'll fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "764||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! Let's do it, Koji!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "765||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh! Ya better be ready for us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "767||||4"
msgid "You're strong...\r\nJoe, too. You've gotten real good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "768||||4"
msgid "I didn't think I'd ever hear that from you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "769||||4"
msgid "Man, ya bastards brought down the TenCozy tag team...\r\nNobody's done that since Okada took us on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "770||||4"
msgid "Before you guys joined JUSTIS, you were\r\nin the color gangs, weren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "771||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Your friend Joe here and Okada\r\nhated the color gangs with a burnin' passion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "772||||4"
msgid "That's why they made JUSTIS, y'know.\r\nThey wanted to crush the color gangs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "773||||4"
msgid "We weren't expectin' to lose, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "774||||4"
msgid "And once you lost to them, you disbanded."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "775||||4"
msgid "Went extinct's more like it.\r\nThey pounded us into the goddamn ground."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "776||||4"
msgid "But y'know, we can't help followin' someone\r\nwho's stronger than us. It's our policy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "777||||4"
msgid "Right. We lost to Okada, so we ditched our colors\r\nand moved over to JUSTIS. That's the short of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "778||||4"
msgid "Which brings us to today,\r\nn' our loss to the Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "779||||4"
msgid "Yup, guess we don't got much choice.\r\nWe'll be followin' our policy n' joinin' you guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "780||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "781||||4"
msgid "We just told ya we follow whoever's stronger than us!\r\nYa guys won, so we're on your side now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "782||||4"
msgid "You're not allowed to say no. This's our policy,\r\nso we've gotta do it no matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "783||||4"
msgid "Plus now that we lost to ya,\r\nwe're totally gettin' kicked outta JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "784||||4"
msgid "What do you think...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "785||||4"
msgid "It should be fine.\r\nThere's a weird sort of logic to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "786||||4"
msgid "Reminds me of myself in a way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "787||||4"
msgid "Glad ya get us, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "788||||4"
msgid "Let's kick some ass, yeah?\r\nN' don't worry, we won't hold ya back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "789||||4"
msgid "I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "790||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "791||||4"
msgid "Tanahashi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "792||||4"
msgid "Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "794||||4"
msgid "Who is that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "795||||4"
msgid "Another Lunatic, Tanahashi. He was a good friend.\r\nOne of the only ones who ever understood me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "796||||4"
msgid "Huh, is that so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "797||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I'd rather not fight him if I can help it...\r\nBut we don't have much choice here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "798||||4"
msgid "Man, there's nothing harder than\r\nhaving to fight your friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "800||||4"
msgid "Maybe so. But sometimes it's easier\r\nto let your fists express how you feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "801||||4"
msgid "I hope that's the case for you and Okada.\r\nIt would be nice if you two made up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "802||||4"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "803||||4"
msgid "Your men are strong, Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "804||||4"
msgid "Tana..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "805||||4"
msgid "Color me impressed, Joe. You've grown\r\nquite a bit since leaving the JUSTIS ranks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "806||||4"
msgid "I don't care about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "807||||4"
msgid "Tana. Don't you realize? JUSTIS is no different\r\nfrom the shitty color gangs back in the day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "808||||4"
msgid "...I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "809||||4"
msgid "Then why are you throwing your weight behind\r\nOkada? We need to show him this is wrong!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "810||||4"
msgid "You're right.\r\nHe may well be out of line."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "811||||4"
msgid "Even so, I promised I would follow him...\r\nand I intend to keep that promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "812||||4"
msgid "But why!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "813||||4"
msgid "Answer me this. Have you ever considered\r\nhow it is he grew to be this way?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "814||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "815||||4"
msgid "It may seem evil from your point of view."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "816||||4"
msgid "But to him,\r\nit's his own personal brand of justice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "817||||4"
msgid "And I agree with it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "818||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "819||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I think that's enough for now.\r\nWe can end here for today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "820||||4"
msgid "Remember, we're enemies.\r\nOur next meeting will be in battle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "821||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Tana!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "822||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "823||||4"
msgid "I need to know. What changed\r\nOkada into the man he is now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "824||||4"
msgid "Didn't we crush the color gangs?\r\nWhy does he need more power than that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "825||||4"
msgid "And also... Why do you stand by him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "826||||4"
msgid "If you want to know... You'll have to defeat me.\r\nGoodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "827||||4"
msgid "Goddammit.\r\nHow did things turn out like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "828||||4"
msgid "Joe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "829||||4"
msgid "It's time for the next Lunatic, Tanahashi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "830||||4"
msgid "Yeah... But I'm not really feeling it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "831||||4"
msgid "Tana was my friend. And he's\r\nevery bit as strong as Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "832||||4"
msgid "This is gonna be a struggle, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "833||||4"
msgid "Tanahashi... He looked like he was\r\nan incredibly reserved man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "834||||4"
msgid "You know, he didn't use to be so serious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "835||||4"
msgid "He used to play a real mean air guitar, or would shout\r\n\"I love you!\" for no reason. Pretty weird, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "836||||4"
msgid "That's a bit of an understatement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "837||||4"
msgid "He really is a great person deep down, though.\r\nHe's never been as restrained as he is now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "838||||4"
msgid "When exactly did he start changing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "839||||4"
msgid "Probably around the same time as Okada. Something\r\nmust have happened between the two of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "842||||4"
msgid "Hey, if we beat this Tanahashi guy, he's gonna\r\ntell us everything that happened, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "843||||4"
msgid "Yeah. We can't afford to lose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "844||||4"
msgid "Hearing what he has to say will be the first step\r\ntoward learning the truth about Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "845||||4"
msgid "All right! We gotta make sure\r\nwe give this our all, then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "846||||4"
msgid "Damn right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "847||||4"
msgid "I never thought the day would come\r\nthat we'd have to fight, Tana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "848||||4"
msgid "Same goes for me, Joe.\r\nWe... used to be so close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "849||||4"
msgid "Don't forget your promise. If we beat you here,\r\nyou'll tell us whatever we want to know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "850||||4"
msgid "Yeah, a deal is a deal.\r\nI'm warning you, though. It won't be easy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "851||||4"
msgid "I'm going to devote every ounce\r\nof my strength to winning here today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "852||||4"
msgid "Even against you...\r\nI don't plan on holding back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "853||||4"
msgid "Don't give me that. You've never really been\r\none for self-restraint in the past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "854||||4"
msgid "I guess you're right, Joe.\r\nYou know me well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "855||||4"
msgid "I love that side of you.\r\nHonestly, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "856||||4"
msgid "Hmph."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "857||||4"
msgid "Now then, the time for talking is over. Let's begin.\r\nI'm going to show you the strength of the Six Lunatics!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "858||||4"
msgid "You're pretty tough, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "859||||4"
msgid "Same to you, Tana.\r\nWe've got you cornered, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "860||||4"
msgid "Not yet you don't.\r\nI was just giving you a little handicap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "861||||4"
msgid "Let's settle this one-on-one.\r\nSee who comes out on top."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "862||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "863||||4"
msgid "Tanahashi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "864||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "865||||4"
msgid "How pathetic, being defeated by these fools.\r\nIt seems we'll have to clean up your mess for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "866||||4"
msgid "Now then... Beat these two to death!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "867||||4"
msgid "You can't just butt in when we're about\r\nto settle things. This isn't your fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "868||||4"
msgid "There are tons of them...\r\nKiryu-san, you gonna be okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "869||||4"
msgid "Absolutely. What about you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "870||||4"
msgid "Absolutely."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "871||||4"
msgid "Good. Watch my back, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "872||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I won't let you down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "873||||4"
msgid "You've done well to reach this point.\r\nHowever, it's just about time to wrap up this party."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "874||||4"
msgid "Move out! Slice these two to pieces!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "875||||4"
msgid "Let's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "876||||4"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "878||||4"
msgid "Guess I lose, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "879||||4"
msgid "You really are strong though, Tana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "880||||4"
msgid "What useless garbage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "881||||4"
msgid "You promised. Tell me everything\r\nyou know about Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "882||||4"
msgid "Right. Honestly, I wanted to\r\nfind a way to talk about this sooner."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "883||||4"
msgid "That's my cue to leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "884||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "885||||4"
msgid "This should stay between friends. I'm sure you\r\ntwo have a lot to catch up on. Take your time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "886||||4"
msgid "I'll be waiting back at the hideout."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "887||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "888||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Joe.\r\nDid Tanahashi fill you in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "889||||4"
msgid "Yeah. He told me everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "890||||4"
msgid "Well? Let's hear it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "891||||4"
msgid "Hm, where should I start?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "892||||4"
msgid "I told you how the reason we made JUSTIS to begin\r\nwith was to take down the color gangs, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "893||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "894||||4"
msgid "At the start, JUSTIS was a tiny organization.\r\nWe quickly gained followers, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "895||||4"
msgid "People all over the city were upset\r\nwith the color gangs reign of terror."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "896||||4"
msgid "Thanks to Okada's charisma, we had\r\na pretty constant stream of new members."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "897||||4"
msgid "We were lacking in numbers,\r\nbut had a wealth of team unity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "898||||4"
msgid "And once we grew big enough...\r\nwe finally took the color gangs out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "899||||4"
msgid "Things were still going well at that point, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "900||||4"
msgid "But soon after, Okada changed and turned\r\nJUSTIS into the gang it is today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "901||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "902||||4"
msgid "And the reason for that?\r\nDid he give you one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "903||||4"
msgid "We destroyed the color gangs, but I guess the\r\nguys pulling the strings were none too happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "904||||4"
msgid "The ones pulling the strings?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "906||||4"
msgid "Yakuza and mafia guys, no doubt. The gangs were\r\njust proxies for them to commit their crimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "907||||4"
msgid "And once the pawns were removed...\r\nThey were probably furious, I'd guess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "908||||4"
msgid "So they wanted retaliation for what you did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "909||||4"
msgid "Yeah. And the one they went after...\r\nwas Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "910||||4"
msgid "Yeah. They got hold of Okada soon after.\r\nPut him through some horrible torture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "911||||4"
msgid "It wasn't just him, though. They apparently\r\neven scarred up his girlfriend real bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "912||||4"
msgid "That's horrible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "913||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "914||||4"
msgid "And after all that happened,\r\nOkada didn't tell any of you about it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "915||||4"
msgid "Yeah. If we knew how bad it was, we would\r\nhave definitely tried to fight back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "916||||4"
msgid "But if we had, more and more people\r\nwould've been tortured just like Okada was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "917||||4"
msgid "I think that's why he stayed quiet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "918||||4"
msgid "Tanahashi figured it all out, though. Accidentally\r\nwalked in on Okada crying about his girlfriend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "919||||4"
msgid "Once he witnessed that, he felt like\r\nhe had to stand by Okada no matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "920||||4"
msgid "So that's how it happened..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "921||||4"
msgid "That's right. I'd known him for years at that point,\r\nbut I'd never seen him look so somber before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "922||||4"
msgid "Tanahashi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "923||||4"
msgid "That day... That's when Okada changed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "924||||4"
msgid "He formed JUSTIS to protect what was important\r\nto him, but he couldn't even keep his girlfriend safe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "925||||4"
msgid "Okada took the blame for that personally.\r\nHe thought JUSTIS wasn't strong enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "926||||4"
msgid "Strength became his only goal. So, he brought in\r\nanyone he deemed strong, even if they were evil."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "927||||4"
msgid "The brawny Tenzan and Kojima. The secretive Naito.\r\nKomei for military, and Yano for fundraising."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "928||||4"
msgid "But that ruined him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "929||||4"
msgid "His team no longer stood for justice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "930||||4"
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "931||||4"
msgid "And all I've done is talk about his wrongdoing,\r\nbut I didn't know the heavy burden he shouldered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "932||||4"
msgid "I'm a failure of a friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "933||||4"
msgid "So what are you going to do?\r\nDo you want to stop going after JUSTIS?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "935||||4"
msgid "No. I won't stop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "936||||4"
msgid "I... I think I know how Okada felt.\r\nHe must have been sad. Depressed, even."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "937||||4"
msgid "Even so, what Okada's been doing now is no better\r\nthan the torture those guys inflicted on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "938||||4"
msgid "He gained power to protect the people around him,\r\nbut he's hurting others at the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "939||||4"
msgid "He's brought forth a second and third\r\nterrible version of himself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "940||||4"
msgid "Joe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "941||||4"
msgid "He's strong, though. And charismatic.\r\nNot only was he a friend, but a role model, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "942||||4"
msgid "That's why... I need to get him back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "943||||4"
msgid "It's my job as a friend.\r\nI need to correct his wrongdoing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "944||||4"
msgid "Joe... You've really grown."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "945||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "946||||4"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "947||||4"
msgid "Joe. Being friends with someone is more\r\nthan just fun and games all the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "948||||4"
msgid "If they do something wrong, you get mad at them.\r\nIf they lose control, you do what it takes to stop them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "949||||4"
msgid "Most importantly, you have to be willing to drop\r\neverything for them. That's what a true friend does."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "950||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "951||||4"
msgid "We've gotten all different types in the\r\nKiryu Clan, but only you can stop him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "952||||4"
msgid "Don't forget that. And...\r\nMake sure your emotions get through to him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "953||||4"
msgid "Make sure you're ready for\r\nwhatever happens, Joe. Understood?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "954||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "955||||4"
msgid "Joe. Kiryu-san.\r\nPlease let me help you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "956||||4"
msgid "You sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "957||||4"
msgid "As I was listening to the two\r\nof you talk, I realized something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "958||||4"
msgid "Even though I thought I was supporting Okada...\r\nI think I was cornering him the whole time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "959||||4"
msgid "Tana..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "960||||4"
msgid "A true pal would stop his friend from doing\r\nsomething wrong. That's clear to me now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "961||||4"
msgid "And... Okada's definitely one of my friends.\r\nLet's bring him down together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "962||||4"
msgid "Tana... Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "964||||4"
msgid "Huh, I think some of my energy's coming back.\r\nIt's almost like my old self's gonna pop right out of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "965||||4"
msgid "That sounds kinda gross, Tana.\r\nThough... I'm glad to hear you're back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "966||||4"
msgid "All right! Now that I'm joining up with you guys,\r\nI've gotta make sure you know how I feel!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "967||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the Kiryu Clan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "968||||4"
msgid "I love you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "969||||4"
msgid "What's with this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "970||||4"
msgid "Sorry. This is more like how Tana usually is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "971||||4"
msgid "Hmph. I guess if nothing else, he'll bring\r\na little bit of cheer to our side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "972||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "973||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. I'm going to save Okada,\r\nno matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "974||||4"
msgid "He's... a close friend, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "975||||4"
msgid "Please lend me your strength,\r\nat least until then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "976||||4"
msgid "Of course. If it means keeping your\r\nfriendship alive, I'll do whatever it takes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "977||||4"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "978||||4"
msgid "Oh, such a pretty little lady!\r\nI love you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "979||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Who the heck is this guy!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "980||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "981||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "982||||4"
msgid "The only ones left in Kamurocho\r\nat this point are Okada and Komei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "983||||4"
msgid "There are still some JUSTIS guys down in Onomichi,\r\nthough. Let's focus on getting rid of them first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "984||||4"
msgid "Next time you head back down there,\r\nwe'll be following right behind you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "985||||4"
msgid "When you have the chance,\r\nstop by the hideout in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "986||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "987||||4"
msgid "Who the heck are<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "988||||4"
msgid "Masao!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "989||||4"
msgid "How lovely it is to see you, Kiryu Clan.\r\nWe appreciate the welcome party, truly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "990||||4"
msgid "Okada..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "991||||4"
msgid "Been a while, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "992||||4"
msgid "Okada. Can we go somewhere else?\r\nI want to talk to you in private."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "993||||4"
msgid "What a brazen fool you are.\r\nRainmaker has no need to speak to you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "994||||4"
msgid "Now then, we are not here to\r\ntrade idle barbs with you buffoons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "995||||4"
msgid "We've come to deliver your final warning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "996||||4"
msgid "Final warning?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "997||||4"
msgid "Indeed. The stage is set for the ultimate battle\r\nbetween you miscreants and the forces of JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "998||||4"
msgid "To be honest, I didn't expect Joe and a washed-up\r\nyakuza would ever manage to make it this far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "999||||4"
msgid "But your glory days are coming to an end.\r\nJUSTIS will bring the curtain down on your lives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1000||||4"
msgid "While you have focused on expanding influence,\r\nwe instead chose to solidify our core."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1001||||4"
msgid "We are stronger now than we've ever been before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1002||||4"
msgid "Furthermore, all that strength is concentrated in\r\nKamurocho. You have no hope of victory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1003||||4"
msgid "We are on a far higher level than you rats!\r\nDo you understand!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1004||||4"
msgid "We'll never know if that's true unless we fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1005||||4"
msgid "How can you even begin to think that!?\r\nThat's why you're nothing but a fool!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1006||||4"
msgid "The only foolish thing possible would be\r\ngiving up without even trying to win."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1007||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu... This is all your fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1008||||4"
msgid "Joe coming back. The Six Lunatics failing me.\r\nYou are to blame for every last thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1009||||4"
msgid "The way you cling to your beliefs\r\nso tightly... It makes me sick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1010||||4"
msgid "This next battle will be when the Kiryu Clan\r\ndraws its final breath. I hope you're ready."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1011||||4"
msgid "Hey, Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1012||||4"
msgid "What is it?\r\nDragon of Dojima, Kazuma Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1013||||4"
msgid "You already know the truth, don't you?\r\nWhat you're doing is wrong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1015||||4"
msgid "I don't get it.\r\nWhat's your angle?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1016||||4"
msgid "Would you ask me this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1017||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1018||||4"
msgid "I have no angle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1020||||4"
msgid "The final battle between JUSTIS and the Kiryu Clan\r\nis fast approaching. Let's settle this, once and for all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1021||||4"
msgid "Oh, I almost forgot. Joe, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1022||||4"
msgid "Don't forget to bring your umbrellas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1023||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1024||||4"
msgid "You heard me. I'm going to\r\nmake it rain here in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1025||||4"
msgid "Not with money... but with blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1026||||4"
msgid "After all, I'm the Rainmaker."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1027||||4"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1028||||4"
msgid "So this is really the final battle.\r\nGuess we're gonna end this for good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1029||||4"
msgid "Sounds like it's gonna be epic.\r\nCan't wait to bust some skulls."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1030||||4"
msgid "I've been feelin' outta shape lately, too.\r\nBut that's gonna change now. Let's do this shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1031||||4"
msgid "Come on, you guys.\r\nTranquilo! Chill out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1032||||4"
msgid "This is gonna be the end. We don't need to rush,\r\nso just make sure you're ready first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1033||||4"
msgid "Eh, we don't gotta worry about those weirdos.\r\nThere's a real genius among our ranks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1034||||4"
msgid "Toru Yano!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1035||||4"
msgid "Me, I mean."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1036||||4"
msgid "All right, I'm feeling real good about this!\r\nLet's get pumped up together, for old time's sake!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1037||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the Kiryu Clan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1038||||4"
msgid "I love you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1039||||4"
msgid "The hell? Why didn't anyone do it!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1040||||4"
msgid "Who'd do that stupid shit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1041||||4"
msgid "No way that's ever gonna catch on, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1042||||4"
msgid "You guys are brutal..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1043||||4"
msgid "Okada. We're gonna wake you up for sure!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1044||||4"
msgid "Joe. It's almost time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1045||||4"
msgid "Yeah. It's only because of you that\r\nwe've come this far, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1046||||4"
msgid "This will be the final battle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1047||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1048||||4"
msgid "All right, everyone. It's time for our showdown\r\nwith JUSTIS. Are you all ready?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1049||||4"
msgid "Course we are! We've come this far,\r\nso we're totally gonna win!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1050||||4"
msgid "Do you have anything to say, Joe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1051||||4"
msgid "I never expected we'd actually be able to go\r\ntoe-to-toe with a powerful enemy like JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1053||||4"
msgid "We're only here because of all of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1054||||4"
msgid "And because of Kiryu-san, who took it upon\r\nhimself to knock me back into shape."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1056||||4"
msgid "As one of JUSTIS's founders, I have to\r\ntake responsibility. I'll destroy them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1057||||4"
msgid "Now, this is our last fight. Please lend me\r\nyour strength, just a little longer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1058||||4"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1059||||4"
msgid "We're gonna give 'em all we got!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1060||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! Let's crush these shits, Koji!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1061||||4"
msgid "Damn straight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1062||||4"
msgid "Come on, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1063||||4"
msgid "Okay. Kiryu Clan... Move out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1064||||4"
msgid "Gotcha!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1065||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1066||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1067||||4"
msgid "Mhm!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1068||||4"
msgid "Si!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1069||||4"
msgid "Good to see you, my Kiryu Clan friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1070||||4"
msgid "I expected you all to run far, far away, but\r\nit seems your stupidity has gotten the best of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1071||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1072||||4"
msgid "Okada..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1073||||4"
msgid "Now then... It's almost time to bring Kiryu Clan\r\nblood raining down on the streets of Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1074||||4"
msgid "Is there anything you'd like to say\r\nbefore we begin, Rainmaker?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1075||||4"
msgid "Nah... I'm good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1076||||4"
msgid "Just as I would have thought. \r\nAre you ready, Kiryu Clan? It's time to die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1077||||4"
msgid "I-Impossible! Our military strength should\r\nhave overwhelmed them easily... Why!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1078||||4"
msgid "There's more to a team than just\r\nhow many members you have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1079||||4"
msgid "You have to like them, trust them,\r\nform bonds with them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1080||||4"
msgid "If you do that, one plus one will be more than two.\r\nIt'll reach one or two hundred."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1081||||4"
msgid "Your inability to see the value in that\r\nis why you lost here today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1083||||4"
msgid "Komei..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1084||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1085||||4"
msgid "Come here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1086||||4"
msgid "Huh? A-Are you sure that's what you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1087||||4"
msgid "Yes. It's up to you now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1088||||4"
msgid "O-Okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1089||||4"
msgid "Joe. Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1090||||4"
msgid "You two are something special."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1091||||4"
msgid "I sold my soul to the devil for JUSTIS,\r\nbut you still managed to stop me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1092||||4"
msgid "And... you did it with true justice\r\nby your side. I envy that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1093||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1094||||4"
msgid "However, I have my own way of doing things.\r\nIt's not time to surrender to you yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1095||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika. Tana told me about\r\neverything that happened to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1096||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry I wasn't there to help.\r\nI wish I had realized sooner."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1097||||4"
msgid "But no matter what happened, resorting to\r\nthe same shit the colors did isn't right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1098||||4"
msgid "Let's start fresh, Kazuchika! JUSTIS can work\r\nfor the good of Kamurocho, like it did before!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1099||||4"
msgid "Are you finished?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1100||||4"
msgid "Okada..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1101||||4"
msgid "Joe. There's something I still need to do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1102||||4"
msgid "And in order to do it...\r\nI need to defeat you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1103||||4"
msgid "This is my last stand.\r\nTry to stop me, Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1104||||4"
msgid "If you really think you can defeat\r\nRainmaker, come on and fight me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1105||||4"
msgid "Fine, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1106||||4"
msgid "It looks like talking isn't going to get us anywhere.\r\nWe'll have to let our fists show him how we feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1107||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Let's take them down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1108||||4"
msgid "No need to tell me twice.\r\nI've never turned down a fight in my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1109||||4"
msgid "Let's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1110||||4"
msgid "Bring it on, Kazuchika!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1115||||4"
msgid "I've lost, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1116||||4"
msgid "In all the fights we've had,\r\nthis is the first time I've won."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1117||||4"
msgid "Is it, now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1118||||4"
msgid "Losers tend to remember their losses, you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1119||||4"
msgid "I see... I suppose I'll always \r\nremember this day, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1120||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kazuchika. JUSTIS is finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1121||||4"
msgid "So I'm going to ask you again.\r\nLet's start over, together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1122||||4"
msgid "We can fight with justice on our side.\r\nYou down?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1123||||4"
msgid "No, not yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1124||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1125||||4"
msgid "There's still something I need to do.\r\nIt's almost time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1126||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1127||||4"
msgid "You really think JUSTIS is finished?\r\nThat's quite a foolish thing to say, Joe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1128||||4"
msgid "Komei!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1129||||4"
msgid "From now on, I'm in charge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1130||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1131||||4"
msgid "Don't you see?\r\nThe era of Rainmaker is over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1132||||4"
msgid "As the leader of JUSTIS, I will rule over\r\nKamurocho with the city's gangs at my feet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1133||||4"
msgid "What are you taking about?\r\nThere's nobody left in JUSTIS!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1134||||4"
msgid "Oh, I suppose I did say we used all our forces.\r\nThat was nothing but a lie, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1135||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1136||||4"
msgid "In truth, I've been buying the loyalty of\r\nJUSTIS's members with the help of a wealthy patron."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1137||||4"
msgid "Buying them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1138||||4"
msgid "Yes. Our organization consists of countless youths\r\nwho only came onboard after being charmed by Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1139||||4"
msgid "But after slipping them a little bit of cash,\r\nit was simple getting them to join my cause instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1140||||4"
msgid "The ones you've beaten so far are only those\r\nwho refused me and stayed loyal to Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1141||||4"
msgid "A large portion of the team has betrayed Okada.\r\nTheir allegiance now rests with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1142||||4"
msgid "JUSTIS isn't over yet. If anything, we're only\r\nnow beginning as a new organization."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1143||||4"
msgid "You bastard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1144||||4"
msgid "What about that wealthy patron\r\nyou were talking about? Who is he?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1145||||4"
msgid "As for that wealthy patron of mine,\r\nallow me to introduce him to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1146||||4"
msgid "Please step over here, Satsuki-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1147||||4"
msgid "Long time no see, Okada."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1148||||4"
msgid "You..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1149||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika... Who is this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1150||||4"
msgid "He's the one who tortured me. And the one\r\nwho assaulted my girlfriend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1151||||4"
msgid "Guess I went a bit overboard back then.\r\nI feel bad. Hurts the heart, you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1152||||4"
msgid "Although, that pain's what pushed you to\r\nturn JUSTIS into what it is today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1153||||4"
msgid "If anything, you should be thanking me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1154||||4"
msgid "Although... I'll be taking back JUSTIS\r\nnow, if you don't mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1155||||4"
msgid "What a sad end for you, Rainmaker."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1156||||4"
msgid "I will take control of JUSTIS and\r\nserve together with Satsuki-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1157||||4"
msgid "Satsuki-san has a great many connections with\r\nthe yakuza and mafia organizations of this town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1158||||4"
msgid "As long as I have his backing, JUSTIS will grow\r\nto be the strongest gang in all of Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1159||||4"
msgid "Komei... Has this been your plan all along?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1160||||4"
msgid "That's right. The only reason I joined JUSTIS\r\nto begin with was to eventually lay claim to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1161||||4"
msgid "I wanted to use Okada to make JUSTIS bigger,\r\nthen snatch it away from him once it got there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1162||||4"
msgid "Then by using JUSTIS, I was going to\r\nget rich beyond your wildest imagination."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1163||||4"
msgid "That was our plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1164||||4"
msgid "Though... I didn't even have to take it from him.\r\nOkada handed me the reins willingly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1165||||4"
msgid "What? So when he whispered in your ear..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1166||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1167||||4"
msgid "You proved a vital asset to my plan, Okada. Things\r\nwould have been far tougher without your trust."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1168||||4"
msgid "Your ignorance to my traitorous nature gave me the\r\ntime I needed to plan this coup. I truly appreciate it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1169||||4"
msgid "You're dumb, though. By not figuring out what was\r\ngoing on, you only propped up my plot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1170||||4"
msgid "You may have charisma, but you clearly\r\nlack the leadership skills to match."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1171||||4"
msgid "Such a shame, Rainmaker!\r\nThe only rain that will be falling today is your tears!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1173||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1176||||4"
msgid "What's wrong?\r\nHas my brilliance driven you mad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1177||||4"
msgid "You two are the ones who have been tricked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1178||||4"
msgid "Everything I've done to make JUSTIS what it is now...\r\nIt was all to draw you out, Satsuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1179||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1180||||4"
msgid "I couldn't forgive you for what you did to me.\r\nI've always vowed to get my revenge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1181||||4"
msgid "But those who live in the shadows are hard to\r\ntrack down. I couldn't begin to get a read on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1182||||4"
msgid "I had to figure out a way to lure you into the open.\r\nThat was how I developed this plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1183||||4"
msgid "To start, I knew you had an affinity for violent\r\ngangs like the way the colors were before us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1184||||4"
msgid "So, if I made another gang similar to them..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1185||||4"
msgid "...You'd come crawling back out of your hole."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1186||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1187||||4"
msgid "I'm surprised you actually fell for it, though.\r\nYou're not as clever as I thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1189||||4"
msgid "I didn't make JUSTIS for the money or the power."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1190||||4"
msgid "It was all so I could get my revenge on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1191||||4"
msgid "Huh. So that was your plan, Kazuchika..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1192||||4"
msgid "S-So then, you already knew I was working\r\nwith Satsuki-san behind your back...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1193||||4"
msgid "Exactly. He knew, and still chose\r\nto let you do your thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1194||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika clearly knew everything you were up\r\nto, including what you were doing with Satsuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1195||||4"
msgid "Right. I suspected every detail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1196||||4"
msgid "Then why... Why did you say you'd\r\nhand me the reins of JUSTIS?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1197||||4"
msgid "Don't you understand, Komei?\r\nYou're just a pawn for Satsuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1198||||4"
msgid "If you didn't have control off the group,\r\nhe'd just cut you off and stay in hiding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1199||||4"
msgid "So that's why... It was so Satsuki-san\r\nwould keep supporting me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1200||||4"
msgid "That's probably it. It would've been a real pain\r\nif Satsuki got away when we were so close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1201||||4"
msgid "As long as you had control of JUSTIS,\r\nKazuchika's plan was still in motion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1202||||4"
msgid "Instead of gaining any real power though,\r\nyou just led us straight to your leader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1203||||4"
msgid "You may be the best strategist around, but\r\nyou clearly don't have the leadership to match."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1204||||4"
msgid "Damn you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1209||||4"
msgid "I don't care about any of this bullshit, as long as\r\nI have obedient soldiers working under me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1210||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... You head up the Kiryu Clan, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1211||||4"
msgid "Yeah, that's right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1212||||4"
msgid "How about you come work for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1213||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1214||||4"
msgid "This fool Komei couldn't manage JUSTIS if his life\r\ndepended on it. Your team is much more promising."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1215||||4"
msgid "As long as you promise obedience...\r\nYou'll find the compensation to your liking. Well?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1216||||4"
msgid "You really expect me to agree to that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1217||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I guess you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1218||||4"
msgid "As expected of the Dragon of Dojima, Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nI apologize for the foolish question."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1219||||4"
msgid "In that case, JUSTIS will have the honor of working\r\nwith me. Together we'll eliminate the Kiryu Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1220||||4"
msgid "And once we do, we'll make sure every suitable\r\nyoung person in Kamurocho joins the JUSTIS cause."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1221||||4"
msgid "They'll become our infantry squad,\r\ncarrying out crimes that rake in the cash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1222||||4"
msgid "And if any of them get caught, they'll take the fall\r\nfor me. I'll go back to my shadows."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1223||||4"
msgid "There's no way...\r\nWe won't let that happen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1224||||4"
msgid "Try to stop me, if you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1225||||4"
msgid "Immature little punk.\r\nYou shouldn't look down at your elders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1226||||4"
msgid "I won't run anymore.\r\nWe'll settle this next time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1227||||4"
msgid "With my own Satsuki Clan forces and JUSTIS\r\ncombined, we'll utterly crush you fools!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1228||||4"
msgid "Go ahead and try."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1229||||4"
msgid "I'm old, too. You'll be in trouble if you\r\nlook down on this immature punk, I promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1230||||4"
msgid "Thanks for the advice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1231||||4"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1232||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes, sir!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1233||||4"
msgid "So the true mastermind has finally arrived."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1234||||4"
msgid "Joe. I'm sorry about this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1235||||4"
msgid "If we don't stop him, the youth of this city will\r\nbe at that fool's beck and call forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1236||||4"
msgid "No matter what it takes, I need to\r\nmake sure that doesn't happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1237||||4"
msgid "I'm really sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1238||||4"
msgid "Kazuchika..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1239||||4"
msgid "I should be the one apologizing. I couldn't figure\r\nout your true motive in all this... I'm a terrible friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1240||||4"
msgid "Don't be ridiculous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1241||||4"
msgid "Besides, I always believed you would\r\nattempt to stop JUSTIS in order to help me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1242||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1243||||4"
msgid "You mean you planned my part in this, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1244||||4"
msgid "More or less. I figured if you shook things up, Komei\r\nand Satsuki would show themselves eventually."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1245||||4"
msgid "That's why I forced you out of JUSTIS.\r\nTo make sure you had the motivation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1246||||4"
msgid "Man, you're incredible.\r\nAre you a fortune teller or something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1247||||4"
msgid "Not quite. Not even I could foresee the\r\nlegendary Dragon of Dojima joining you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1249||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. My apologies for everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1250||||4"
msgid "If it's all right with you,\r\nI'd like to join your team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1251||||4"
msgid "I need to defeat that man.\r\nI... I need to get my revenge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1252||||4"
msgid "Okada..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1253||||4"
msgid "Okay, then.\r\nLet's take him down together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1254||||4"
msgid "Thank you very much, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1255||||4"
msgid "All right. This next battle will be our last."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1256||||4"
msgid "With the Kiryu Clan behind us,\r\nwe'll destroy them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1257||||4"
msgid "You two should get ready, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1258||||4"
msgid "Of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1259||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1260||||4"
msgid "All right, our battle with Satsuki is finally here.\r\nAre you ready, everyone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1261||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1262||||4"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1263||||4"
msgid "This really will be the final battle.\r\nI want to thank you all for trusting in me so far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1264||||4"
msgid "However, failure here means losing everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1265||||4"
msgid "If they win, they'll carry out their plan to turn\r\nthe youth of this city into an army of criminal soldiers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1266||||4"
msgid "Under no circumstance can we let that happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1267||||4"
msgid "We're going to win... And we're going to\r\ndrive them out of Kamurocho for good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1268||||4"
msgid "Its future rests in our hands. The young people here\r\nshould be out making friends, not committing crimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1269||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... I'm so thankful I met you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1270||||4"
msgid "Same for me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1271||||4"
msgid "Now let's go. The final battle awaits!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1272||||4"
msgid "Right. Kiryu Clan, move out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1273||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1274||||4"
msgid "There are so many of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1275||||4"
msgid "I guess they're the combined forces of\r\nJUSTIS and the Satsuki Clan, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1276||||4"
msgid "What's wrong? Are you nervous?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1277||||4"
msgid "Not at all.\r\nIf anything, I'm excited."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1278||||4"
msgid "I'm really looking forward to fighting\r\nalongside my friend here again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1279||||4"
msgid "You better not slow me down, Joe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1280||||4"
msgid "I should be saying that to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1281||||4"
msgid "Nice to see you, my Kiryu Clan friends.\r\nToday is the day that all of you die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1282||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho will be taken by myself and Satsuki-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1283||||4"
msgid "Dreams... Bonds... Admiration..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1284||||4"
msgid "By outwardly espousing those foolish ideals,\r\nwe'll form the largest gang in all of Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1285||||4"
msgid "And as the first step toward that ultimate goal,\r\nwe'll be using you Kiryu Clan buffoons as a sacrifice!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1286||||4"
msgid "Now then, the last dance is finally beginning.\r\nGo! Tear the Kiryu Clan to shreds!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1287||||4"
msgid "We have him on the ropes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1288||||4"
msgid "I've waited a long time for this day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1289||||4"
msgid "My grudge against you is finally going to be repaid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1290||||4"
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1291||||4"
msgid "There's still more of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1292||||4"
msgid "Okada. You think you're the king of the world,\r\nbut you're just a little brat in the end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1293||||4"
msgid "You have no idea how dangerous the world\r\nof men can truly be. I'll have to show you myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1294||||4"
msgid "Just like I did so many years ago!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1295||||4"
msgid "You bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1296||||4"
msgid "And as for this \"justice\" you guys talk so highly of...\r\nYou're going to see just how ineffective it really is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1297||||4"
msgid "You're going to pay for what you did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1298||||4"
msgid "I'm here to help, friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1299||||4"
msgid "Heh... You two remind me a bit of\r\nmyself when I was your age."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1300||||4"
msgid "Huh? Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1301||||4"
msgid "Yeah. When you asked me to be the leader of\r\nyou kids, I thought it was just more trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1302||||4"
msgid "I wasn't into the idea of sticking my neck out,\r\nbut I did, because you made me want to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1303||||4"
msgid "You reminded me of the values I've always\r\nheld at my core."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1304||||4"
msgid "The importance of friends, the justice within us...\r\nThey might sound childish, but they're vital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1305||||4"
msgid "I must have forgotten over the years, but those things\r\nare clear to me again because of you. Thanks for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1306||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1307||||4"
msgid "Even after this battle ends, make sure\r\nyou remember the value of those concepts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1308||||4"
msgid "Once you forget them, you tend to age a lot quicker.\r\nTrust me on that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1309||||4"
msgid "Right! I'll remember both you and\r\nthe events of today, for as long as I live!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1310||||4"
msgid "Then we'll have to make it a memory worth keeping.\r\nCome on! Let's stop this madman in his tracks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1311||||4"
msgid "You wanna disband the Kiryu Clan!?\r\nAre you being serious right now!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1312||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Not only did we beat JUSTIS,\r\nbut their mastermind Satsuki as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1313||||4"
msgid "Thanks to Satsuki's arrest, the police have\r\nmanaged to round up most of his followers as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1314||||4"
msgid "It just doesn't seem necessary to continue on\r\nwith the Kiryu Clan at this point. Am I wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1315||||4"
msgid "Way too wrong! What're you thinking!?\r\nThe Kiryu Clan's where all of us belong now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1316||||4"
msgid "Really...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1317||||4"
msgid "Yeah, that's right! We can't just let it fade away\r\nnow that we've fulfilled our initial goal!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1318||||4"
msgid "The Kiryu Clan's, well... I dunno how to put this...\r\nIt's like some kinda family to me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1319||||4"
msgid "Well said, Masao-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1320||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1321||||4"
msgid "I've gotta agree with him, Kiryu-san.\r\nLet's keep the Kiryu Clan going for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1322||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho isn't known for its tranquility.\r\nAnother Satsuki or JUSTIS will sprout up eventually."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1323||||4"
msgid "We can be a place to protect the youth from bastards\r\nlike that. That's why we need the Kiryu Clan to continue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1324||||4"
msgid "I want to build the organization Kazuchika\r\nand I strived for. The original JUSTIS."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1325||||4"
msgid "A team with justice at their side... JUSTIS..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1326||||4"
msgid "Okay. If it's that important to you,\r\nI'm okay with keeping the Kiryu Clan intact."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1327||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah!\r\nThanks for understanding, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1328||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! I love you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1329||||4"
msgid "We're gonna be part of something special\r\ntogether for years to come, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1330||||4"
msgid "Yeah. By the way, there's something I've\r\nbeen wondering for a long time now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1331||||4"
msgid "What's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1332||||4"
msgid "The spelling of JUSTIS.\r\nI mean, shouldn't it be j-u-s-t-i-c-e?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1333||||4"
msgid "Why'd you choose j-u-s-t-i-s?\r\nIt was intentional, right...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1334||||4"
msgid "Huh? Wait, did we misspell it?\r\nHoly shit... That's lame..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1335||||4"
msgid "What? You seriously just spelled it wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1336||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah. We really messed up, Kazuchika."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1337||||4"
msgid "I-I guess so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1338||||4"
msgid "Well, maybe Kiryu-san has it wrong..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1339||||4"
msgid "My English is nothing to write home about,\r\nbut even I know that word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1340||||4"
msgid "It's pretty common in song lyrics, you know.\r\nI'm sure I'm right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1341||||4"
msgid "How didn't anyone notice this before now!?\r\nGood thing we disbanded JUSTIS then, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1342||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1343||||4"
msgid "Hey hey, what're you little idiots\r\nchattin' about over here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1344||||4"
msgid "What's up, Yano?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1345||||4"
msgid "Some of those mastermind guy's followers\r\nand leftover JUSTIS shits're causin' some trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1346||||4"
msgid "So there're still a few left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1347||||4"
msgid "C'mon, Koji!\r\nWe're gonna crush 'em all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1348||||4"
msgid "Tranquilo! Chill out, guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1349||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san's our leader, remember?\r\nIt's his choice if we're going or not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1350||||4"
msgid "So Kiryu-san? Whaddya say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1351||||4"
msgid "We don't have much choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1352||||4"
msgid "Looks like we have some garbage to clean up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1353||||4"
msgid "To bring our justice out into the world,\r\nand to protect the youth of this country..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1354||||4"
msgid "...Kiryu Clan, move out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1355||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1356||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1357||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1358||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1359||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1360||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1361||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1362||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1363||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, um... I really have to thank you\r\nfor coming to save me earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1364||||4"
msgid "It was nothing. I'm just glad you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1365||||4"
msgid "Me too! Anyway, um... Joe-san and my brother\r\nreally forced you into this team thing. Sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1366||||4"
msgid "Yeah I don't mind, though.\r\nI've already agreed, so I'll figure something out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1367||||4"
msgid "Although, this is my first time dealing with young\r\nguys like this. How do I attract new members...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1368||||4"
msgid "Oh! I think the bartender would know!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1369||||4"
msgid "Really...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1370||||4"
msgid "He was the leader of a humongous team\r\nback in his days as a thug on the street!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1371||||4"
msgid "Huh... He sounds experienced."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1372||||4"
msgid "Isn't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1373||||4"
msgid "Sachiko... How can you be so disrespectful?\r\nI'm gonna have to sue you for slander, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1374||||4"
msgid "But Kiryu-san said he needs to scrape\r\ntogether some new members for his team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1375||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? That's a cinch.\r\nJust give 'em a good whack on the head!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1376||||4"
msgid "You want me to hit them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1377||||4"
msgid "Heck yeah. Some of the kids around these parts\r\nact like they own the goddamn place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1378||||4"
msgid "It's one of the flaws of the countryside. They all\r\nthink they're the strongest little shit around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1379||||4"
msgid "Ugh, so they're just puffed up idiots."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1380||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I'm pretty sure they'll follow anyone\r\nwho can prove they're stronger, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1381||||4"
msgid "So if you knock them flat on their asses, Kiryu-san,\r\nI bet they'll follow you no questions asked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1382||||4"
msgid "Huh!? That's kinda violent, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1383||||4"
msgid "That's right. I'm not the young guy I used to be.\r\nI can't just go around punching people nowadays."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1384||||4"
msgid "I don't think you'll need to worry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1385||||4"
msgid "Why do you say that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1386||||4"
msgid "These guys'll come to you once\r\nthey see how strong you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1387||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Are you sure!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1388||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you're a damn skilled fighter.\r\nThat's clear as day to anyone with experience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1389||||4"
msgid "If someone who's itching for a fight catches sight\r\nof you, there's no way they'll be able to resist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1390||||4"
msgid "You think so? I can't really tell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1391||||4"
msgid "Absolutely! Even I'm getting in the mood..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1392||||4"
msgid "Huh? This is no time for that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1393||||4"
msgid "I'm just joking around! But seriously, try it out.\r\nYou'll find potential members all over town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1394||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1395||||4"
msgid "You used to live in Tokyo, right Kiryu-san?\r\nI'm so jealous..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1396||||4"
msgid "Tokyo's really an incredible place, huh?\r\nIt's so different from Onomichi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1397||||4"
msgid "Tokyo's such an amazing place.\r\nMaybe I'll apply to universities up there..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1398||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Look after my brother again today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1399||||4"
msgid "Welcome, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1400||||4"
msgid "Thanks a bunch!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1401||||4"
msgid "Please come back soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1402||||4"
msgid "Everything the bartender cooks up is so tasty!\r\nHe might look scary, but he has tons of skill."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1403||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Please take this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1404||||4"
msgid "Good luck out there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1405||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! What do you want to do today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1406||||4"
msgid "Huh? The shit you think you're looking at?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1407||||4"
msgid "You look kinda strong for an old fuck, though.\r\nShow me what you got!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1408||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whoa... I had no idea people\r\nthat strong even existed..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1409||||4"
msgid "I wanna be just like you, old man.\r\nPlease lemme be your apprentice!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1410||||4"
msgid "Huh? What're ya lookin' at, old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1411||||4"
msgid "Oh, you actually look pretty tough. I'm kinda bored.\r\nHow 'bout you help me kill some time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1412||||4"
msgid "You're damn strong..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1413||||4"
msgid "Sorry 'bout that. Here, I'll fight for ya\r\nto make up for it. Just forgive me, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1414||||4"
msgid "Huh? Who the hell're you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1415||||4"
msgid "If you got something you want from me...\r\nyou're gonna have to fight me first!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1416||||4"
msgid "H-Holy shit, you're strong.\r\nI'm so sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1417||||4"
msgid "I-I'll do anything ya want.\r\nPlease teach me how to be stronger!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1418||||4"
msgid "Sup, grampa?\r\nYou wanna pick a fight with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1419||||4"
msgid "How 'bout that. I've been lookin' for\r\nsomeone who'll make me break a sweat! C'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1420||||4"
msgid "I-I give. Just forgive me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1421||||4"
msgid "You're real tough, man. With you teaching me,\r\nwho knows how strong I'll get!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1422||||4"
msgid "Hey, you. The hell do you want?\r\nYou trying to pick a fight or something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1423||||4"
msgid "Fine by me. I'm the strongest in all of Onomichi.\r\nI'm gonna beat you to a bloody pulp!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1424||||4"
msgid "Damn, that's some strength.\r\nYou're incredible. Admirable, even."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1425||||4"
msgid "My motto's always been to follow anyone stronger\r\nthan me, so... I guess I'll be sticking by you for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1426||||4"
msgid "And who might you be?\r\nDo you have a problem with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1427||||4"
msgid "You have a strong air about you. I expect\r\nyou'll be a tough opponent. Fight me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1428||||4"
msgid "What impressive strength...\r\nIt appears I need far more training."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1429||||4"
msgid "Would it be all right if I came to train under you?\r\nI would love to grow stronger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1430||||4"
msgid "Look what we got here! Some kinda outsider, huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1431||||4"
msgid "Y'shouldn't be walkin' around here lookin' so tough!\r\nYer gonna have t'pay the price, with yer body!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1432||||4"
msgid "What the hell are ya!?\r\nNobody in Onomichi's anywhere close t'ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1433||||4"
msgid "Maybe I can get stronger if I join up with ya.\r\nAll right, my mind's made up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1434||||4"
msgid "Who're you? I don't recognize your face."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1435||||4"
msgid "You look like you've seen a bit of blood\r\nin your day, though. This should be fun... Let's fight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1436||||4"
msgid "You're strong, man. It's been ages since\r\nI've enjoyed myself in a fight this much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1437||||4"
msgid "I bet I'll have tons more fun if I join you.\r\nSorry, but you'll be seeing a lot more of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1438||||4"
msgid "Oooh. You look damn tough, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1439||||4"
msgid "I've been real bored fighting weak shits lately.\r\nSorry, but you're gonna have to liven things up a bit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1440||||4"
msgid "I lost... Never thought I'd find someone\r\nstronger than me in this small-time town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1441||||4"
msgid "Thanks for showing me the light, buddy.\r\nI'll gladly help you out when you need it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1442||||4"
msgid "Oh? You've got a pretty tough-looking body."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1443||||4"
msgid "Great. You're the perfect guy to test my strength with!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1444||||4"
msgid "Holy crap... You're so strong.\r\nI've gotta admit, I admire that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1445||||4"
msgid "I wanna be strong just like you.\r\nHow about you teach me the ropes a bit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1446||||4"
msgid "Hey, do you have a minute?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1447||||4"
msgid "Can I ask you something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1448||||4"
msgid "I know this might seem random...\r\nbut do you want to join my team?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1449||||4"
msgid "Then join my team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1450||||4"
msgid "Dammit. We couldn't break through their ranks.\r\nGuess we should just withdraw for now, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1451||||4"
msgid "Let's regroup and try to take them on again soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1452||||4"
msgid "Those guys are strong... They might've\r\nreally killed us if we hadn't run away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1453||||4"
msgid "Let's regroup and try to take them on again soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1454||||4"
msgid "Yo, Kiryu-san. Thanks for keeping an eye\r\non these punks. I appreciate it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1455||||4"
msgid "It's nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1456||||4"
msgid "I didn't think they'd actually end up\r\nhelping you out though, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1457||||4"
msgid "To be honest, they kinda remind me\r\nof me back when I was a kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1458||||4"
msgid "Makes me feel all warm n' fuzzy inside.\r\nThat's why I let them use my place as a hideout."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1459||||4"
msgid "Sheesh... I put so much effort making this place\r\nbeautiful, but they just go and cramp my style."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1460||||4"
msgid "You're not wrong there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1461||||4"
msgid "You're different from them though, Kiryu-san.\r\nYou actually order stuff, and even pay for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1462||||4"
msgid "It's a real help. You're basically\r\none o' my regulars at this point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1463||||4"
msgid "I guess you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1464||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. I was thinking of ways I could\r\nmaybe try n' repay you for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1465||||4"
msgid "And well, how 'bout I lend\r\na hand with the Kiryu Clan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1466||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1467||||4"
msgid "Haven't ya heard? I used to be legendary 'round here.\r\nThough I've been getting kinda rusty lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1468||||4"
msgid "Honestly, seeing these punks do their thing takes me\r\nway back to how I used to be when I was young."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1469||||4"
msgid "I'm kinda jealous that you get to be a part\r\nof their whole shindig, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1470||||4"
msgid "All right, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1471||||4"
msgid "Hope I'm not too much trouble.\r\nI'll try not to slow ya guys down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1472||||4"
msgid "N' I'll still be able to run the shop\r\neven if I break all my bones. Don't worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1473||||4"
msgid "This is gonna be good, leader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1474||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but we don't actually have\r\nenough members yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1475||||4"
msgid "Give us a little more time, then come back. Okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1476||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! The Kiryu Clan's getting real big!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1477||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1478||||4"
msgid "If you wanna try fighting against other clans,\r\ntalk to Joe. He said he'll help you out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1479||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1480||||4"
msgid "Yeah. He's pretty damn popular, so he's got\r\nall sortsa special connections."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1481||||4"
msgid "Try it out if you're ever feeling up to it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1482||||4"
msgid "I forgot to mention, Kiryu-san.\r\nYou got any interest in the black market?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1483||||4"
msgid "Uh, guess I should explain first. It's basically a place\r\nyou can go for some... contraband merchandise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1484||||4"
msgid "A friend of mine's in the biz, so I thought\r\nyou might wanna meet up with him, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1485||||4"
msgid "He's got tons of stuff great for fighting.\r\nProbably a perfect kinda shop for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1486||||4"
msgid "I was thinking you'd get some serious use outta\r\na place like that, so whaddya say? Want an intro?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1487||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1488||||4"
msgid "Okay, I'll get in touch with him for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1489||||4"
msgid "This is where he is. Try heading there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1490||||4"
msgid "I'll let you know where he's at once\r\nhe says he's cool with meeting you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1491||||4"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1492||||4"
msgid "Oh! You must be Kiryu-san, huh?\r\nThe La Pente bartender told me about you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1493||||4"
msgid "I usually don't deal to people on our first meeting,\r\nbut I'll make an exception for friends of his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1494||||4"
msgid "You could say we go back a ways.\r\nUsed to get into all sortsa shit together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1495||||4"
msgid "I never would have guessed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1496||||4"
msgid "By the way, I heard you've been spending\r\nsome time up in Kamurocho, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1497||||4"
msgid "I've got a friend up there running a similar outfit.\r\nI'll let him know about you if you wanna check it out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1498||||4"
msgid "The bartender'll message you the location."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1499||||4"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1500||||4"
msgid "Now then... Check out the goods."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1501||||4"
msgid "Come again sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1502||||4"
msgid "Yo, how 'bout a look?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1503||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1504||||4"
msgid "Hey, I got some good stuff in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1505||||4"
msgid "I'm out of that. Sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1506||||4"
msgid "Hm? You're...\r\nOh, you must be Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1507||||4"
msgid "I heard about you.\r\nGot some special stuff for ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1508||||4"
msgid "So, whaddya want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1509||||4"
msgid "Hope to see you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1510||||4"
msgid "Yo, check this out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1511||||4"
msgid "Thanks a ton."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1512||||4"
msgid "Hey, I got some good stuff in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1513||||4"
msgid "I'm out of that. Sorry."
msgstr ""

